svg.desc:
Seamless Rectangles Pattern - Animated
original work: https://openclipart.org/detail/299972/rectangles-pattern and: https://openclipart.org/detail/299973/rectangles-pattern-black
Optimized by removing redundant code, deleting shaded outlines, then merging the code from the black rectangles pattern image
The symbol is reused to make a seamless pattern by flipping it horizontally and vertically
Added animation to show the pattern in different multiples of its size
Edit the code to use the other rectangle to expand beyond its viewBox and fill the screen
Jay Nick STEAMcoded.org
